# No Cursor git attribution

Never add any of the following to commits, commit messages, PR descriptions, or code comments:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor`
- Any other Cursor attribution trailer or footer

When creating git commits, use only the user's identity. Do not append co-author or attribution lines.
